This paper presents a large data set of news items and their social feedback, which is relevant to fields such as information retrieval (cs.IR), recommender systems (cs.SI), data mining (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions potential research areas such as topic detection and tracking (cs.CL), sentiment analysis in short text (cs.CL), first story detection (cs.CY), and news recommendation (cs.IR). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IR and cs.SI, followed by cs.CL, cs.LG, and cs.CY.
